{"tid":1320273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"溫古知新 7警到現在","createTime":"2019-07-15T10:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:45.000Z","uid":279560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4506deb38eb91d3eefc866aa10fe0a596203f7cf","tid":1320273,"uid":279560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:53:39.000Z","msg":"溫古知新,<br />\n柒婆今日話,會促請律政司盡快完成檢控被補人士!<br />\n另我回想起7警案.<br />\n<br />\n7警案,未計審訊時間,由報案到檢控長達一年.其間曾健超多次向警務處要求提供7警資料被拒,後再入稟要求頒令公開7警身份,....之後(看文or google)<br />\n<br />\n今日抗議示威場面,不論便衣警員或是防暴警,都刻意不出示及隱藏身份,所謂何事?<br />\n<br />\n法例要求清晰展示警員委任証,便是要市民大眾都可以對掌公權者進行監督.警員委任証也是提醒每一個擁有此權力者自己應有的責任!<br />\n<br />\n掌握公權力,執法者,高薪厚祿的香港警務人員,是懷著一個什麼的心態上前線工作? <br />\n跟7警一樣準備好隨時違反法例?<br />\n準備好執行私刑,去暴打你前面的所謂敵人?<br />\n要求警員{出示警員委任証}不是一個口號來的,是法例!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20151015/s00001/1444884398504/%e3%80%90%e4%b8%83%e8%ad%a6%e6%a1%88%e4%b8%80%e5%b9%b4%e3%80%91%e5%be%9e%e5%a0%b1%e6%a1%88%e5%88%b0%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20151015%2Fs00001%2F1444884398504%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e4%25b8%2583%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25a1%2588%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25be%259e%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e6%25a1%2588%25e5%2588%25b0%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%258e%25a7&d=mMU56kjTNdUxye0JV9HIjZggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=b6f8f61d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20151015%2Fs00001%2F1444884398504%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e4%25b8%2583%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25a1%2588%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25be%259e%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e6%25a1%2588%25e5%2588%25b0%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e6%258e%25a7&h=b5c4f35f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20151015/s00001/1444884398504/%e3%80%90%e4%b8%83%e8%ad%a6%e6%a1%88%e4%b8%80%e5%b9%b4%e3%80%91%e5%be%9e%e5%a0%b1%e6%a1%88%e5%88%b0%e6%aa%a2%e6%8e%a7</a>"},{"pid":"0d1a8a7b3441ed572ed4629c0ac78de1561ab3da","tid":1320273,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:54:08.000Z","msg":"[求助要人]海富73歲陳伯已絕食9日超過200小時 隻腳有傷口未埋口 點解無人知無人理！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1310102\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1310102</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"18d89b1446d8b77e4a2efc01fdd86111eac26e12","tid":1320273,"uid":130898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T10:55:17.000Z","msg":"屌啦好撚多POST幫佢地洗白 <br />\n又話咩功就白衫領我屌你開OT拎撚左十萬蚊唔係功?<br />\n免費WAR GAME唔係補償?<br />\n佢地有錢收啦唔好當班仆街係義工 <br />\n一係就罷工比我地睇 唔好撚昆鳩我地"},{"pid":"d7ec9df64735191b4312aecba1f68c0d8db73ed2","tid":1320273,"uid":5662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T11:01:45.000Z","msg":"黑警無一個係無辜嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}